user.biography: A Place Like No Other™. Home to 71 rides, including 18 roller coasters, Cedar Point Shores Waterpark and more.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on July 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'h & CREATIONS GLASS THEATER BLOWING HAND D-MA UNIQUE SOUVENIRS'.

node.text:
If rides and roller coasters aren't your thing, there's still plenty to do and see at Cedar Point! 😄 

Enjoy daily shows at the Glass Blowing Theatre where talented artisans demonstrate how to make beautiful creations made entirely out of glass!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on July 17, 2021. May be an image of 5 people, people standing and text that says 'YEARS YEARS'.

node.text:
Have you seen the Celebrate 150 Spectacular show yet? 👀 

Take a journey through Cedar Point's history with live music, dancers, singers and performers galore! The fun starts at 9:30 p.m. in Celebration Plaza every night through August 15! 🙌 
#TheFunisJustBeginning

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on July 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Cedar Point 150 YEARS'.

node.text: Happy #FanFriday! Get your exclusive button this week at The Button Stop along the Main Midway while supplies last!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on July 14, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, child, people standing, outdoors and text that says '50,000th Rider This Season! 20t0 EXPRESS WOCDSTOCK'.

node.text:
Let's celebrate a milestone! Sisters Paislee & Londyn were the 50,000th (and 50,001st) riders on Woodstock Express this season. 

Look out for more milestone riders throughout the season! 👏

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point in Cedar Point. May be an image of nature.
Photo by Cedar Point on July 12, 2021. May be an image of indoor.

node.text:
Skee-ball anyone? Be sure to visit the arcade in the Grand Coliseum to play a newly refurbished classic! 😄 

Not your thing? No worries! There are tons of other new machines to test your skill on, including video games! 🕹️👾

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on July 11, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing and outdoors.

node.text:
Each day we're giving away a Ticket of a Lifetime! 😄 When you see Courtesy Corps kiosks like this one around the park, register and enter for your chance to win! 👏 

You can also win other prizes like exclusive access to VIP areas, including the Lakeside Lounge presented by Platform Beer Co.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on July 10, 2021. May be an image of food, indoor and text that says 'Cedar 150 Point YEARS 1870 2020'.

node.text:
Celebrate Cedar Point's 150th Anniversary by tasting favorite park foods from the past with a modern twist! With locations throughout the park, you can try items like waffle fry nachos, a funnel cake hot chicken sandwich and more! 🍔🌭🥙🍦🍇 

Find out more here: cedarpoint.com/150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on July 09, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text:
When's the last time you visited The Barnyard on the Frontier Trail? 🐫🐄🐴 

Grab a friend and say hi to all of the animals! 🐐🐓🐷

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on July 09, 2021.

node.text: The Queen of American Watering Places is our featured button for Fan Friday! Get yours now at Button Stop before they sell out! 🎢

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cedar Point on July 08, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, people sitting, indoor and outdoors.

node.text:
When you enter for the chance to win a Ticket of a Lifetime, you could win access to the VIP areas, including the Lakeside Lounge presented by Platform Beer Co. 🤩 

Enter to win at any Courtesy Corps kiosk in the park.

node.text: It's Truce Day at Forbidden Frontier on Adventure Island! 🤝 Solve mysteries, interact with island inhabitants and live the adventure for yourself each day 11a - 7p!
